graphics:
	ncurses/derivative for graphics
	filepath at bottom
controls:
	nonmodal (may change later)
	if character not basic ascii -> dont write it
	^s save
	^q quit
	^f search
		^n for next
		^b for previous
	^x run external command
	backspace to delete letter
data:
	array of lines
	(may change, depending on implementation)
